data.description: Home is move-in condition with full basement and finished recreation room. Spacious a guest bedroom and full bath on the main floor. Open floor plan on  the main. Formal Dining Room with hard wood and crown mouldings; Kitchen with attached Keeping room with hardwood floors; Along with breakfast bar and  eat-in area. Family room with fireplace. Upper level features Master Suite and private bath with dual sinks, tile floors and large window for added light.  Additional 2 bedrooms on this level plus an extra room - ideal playroom or office area with hardwood floors. Laundry Room with Sink. Addtl unfinished  storage or expansion areas in basement. Rear Deck, Warranty, Private backyard grounds.
